    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40668022_16_13778-13825",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "13778-13825",
      "markText": "除了再进行征服，已经没有了扩展农业生产的空间。由于临近明朝控制的辽东，经济的出路只能来自那里。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40668022&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=13778&rangeEnd=13825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8932250726c8b76c896891?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=13778&rangeEnd=13825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40668022_80_2120-2197",
      "chapterUid": 80,
      "range": "2120-2197",
      "markText": "但这样一来，“人情互惠”（报）的文化价值观，就阻碍了中国人在伦理上遵循普遍平等的原则；而这一原则，正是马克斯·韦伯和帕森斯所认定的西方社会秩序的核心基础。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40668022&chapterUid=80&rangeStart=2120&rangeEnd=2197",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8932250726c8b76c896891?chapterUid=80&rangeStart=2120&rangeEnd=2197"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40668022_16_24252-24319",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "24252-24319",
      "markText": "努尔哈赤十分看重拥有某种特殊手艺和才能的人在经济上的贡献，比如丝织工人和铁匠。被抓获的朝鲜和汉族工匠常常得到赦免，不管他们是否抵抗过。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40668022&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=24252&rangeEnd=24319",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8932250726c8b76c896891?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=24252&rangeEnd=24319"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40668022_27_2672-2686",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "2672-2686",
      "markText": "这个基础在顺治朝便已然奠定。",
